rthYear'",[38,294,295],{"class":44},", data.",[38,297,189],{"class":48},[38,299,300],{"class":44},"());\n",[38,302,304],{"class":40,"line":303},4,[38,305,173],{"class":44},[17,307,308,309,311],{},"A Static method, on the other hand, runs on top of the Model — so it's kind of like wrapping up your own custom ",[35,310,75],{},":",[28,313,314],{"className":30,"code":124,"language":32,"meta":33,"style":33},[35,315,316,336,348],{"__ignoreMap":33},[38,317,318,320,322,324,326,328,330,332,334],{"class":40,"line":41},[38,319,131],{"class":44},[38,321,49],{"class":48},[38,323,136],{"class":44},[38,325,81],{"class":48},[38,327,84],{"class":44},[38,329,143],{"class":87},[38,331,91],{"class":44},[38,333,94],{"class":52},[38,335,150],{"class":44},[38,337,338,340,342,344,346],{"class":40,"line":62},[38,339,155],{"class":44},[38,341,158],{"class":48},[38,343,161],{"class":44},[38,345,165],{"class":164},[38,347,168],{"class":44},[38,349,350],{"class":40,"line":115},[38,351,173],{"class":44},[17,353,354],{},"And that's the simplest way to think about the difference between Static methods and Instance methods.",[356,357,358],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sj_SG, html code.shiki .sj_SG{--shiki-default:#DBB7FF}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh